---
title: Big Pigs in Blankets and Parsley Mash with Jerk Spiced Veg and Mango Chutney Gravy
description: This Big Pigs in Blankets and Parsley Mash is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
